        "name": "Forager",
        "subtype": "ability",
        "text": "While using Survival to Subsist, if the sentry rolls a failure or a critical failure, they get a success instead. If the sentry rolls a success, they can provide food for 16 additional creatures that eat about as much as a human, or 32 creatures on a critical success.",
